Primal Broo<a href=http://www.primalbrood.org/>d</a></br></c></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/usulvar.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sulvar</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 24<br> <font color=#FF0000>(7/30/02 4:59:37 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthebattlefield.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=1104.topic&index=4>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: How to camp Wavecrusher in SG?</span><hr size=1> Here is how my guild usually gets to the castle where the shimmering spawns.<br>
<br>
1) Zone to SG from CS and evac or succor across to the WW side of the zone.<br>
<br>
2) Work your way to the well and clear all the mobs that are in your path and at the top of the well<br>
<br>
3) Have everyone invis up and have your main tank jump into the well and stop at the first ledge.  Sometimes the sirens there see invis and will agro you.  If they do you will need to kill them.  If they don't have everyone jump into the well invis and swim down and out the bottom of it.<br>
<br>
4) Once you swim out of the well you will be inside what I guess is called the castle area.  It is sort of set up with a huge pool on one side, a large staircase in the middle.  On the sides of this room there is a tiny niche with a single moktor in it.  If you are in the pool facing the staircase this niche is on the right side.  We usually invis to this niche, kill the moktor inside it and then set up camp here.<br>
<br>
5) From here just clear out as many spawns as you can.  The shimmering can spawn in numerous places down here, but I have seen her for sure spawn in the left corner while facing the pool from the niche. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=179608>Gartuff</a>
