<br>
We set up camp at the same point he is referring to.  Its a good spot to camp the WC, and we also got a lot of BP gems.<br>
<br>
The AE dispell on some of the mobs is a pain - stun lock em if you can. <p><a href=http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=331441>Tappy Thistlebloom</a>
